sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant C as Claude
    participant HOT as CLAUDE.md<br/>(Hot Cache)
    participant GLOSS as memory/glossary.md
    participant DEEP as memory/people/<br/>memory/projects/

    U->>C: "Ask Todd about the PSR for Oracle"

    Note over C,HOT: Tier 1 — Hot Cache Lookup
    C->>HOT: Lookup "Todd", "PSR", "Oracle"
    HOT-->>C: Todd = Todd Chen (Finance, VP)<br/>PSR = Pipeline Status Report<br/>Oracle = Oracle Systems (Q2 deal)

    Note over C: All resolved from hot cache
    C-->>U: Decoded: "Ask Todd Chen (Finance VP)<br/>about the Pipeline Status Report<br/>for the Oracle Systems Q2 deal"

    Note over C,HOT: — Alternative: Partial Cache Miss —

    U->>C: "Get Mika's take on DORA for Starfish"
    C->>HOT: Lookup "Mika", "DORA", "Starfish"
    HOT-->>C: Mika = Mika Patel (Eng Lead)<br/>DORA = not found<br/>Starfish = not found

    Note over C,GLOSS: Tier 2 — Glossary Lookup
    C->>GLOSS: Lookup "DORA", "Starfish"
    GLOSS-->>C: DORA = DevOps Research and Assessment<br/>Starfish = not found

    Note over C,DEEP: Tier 3 — Deep Storage
    C->>DEEP: Search memory/projects/ for "Starfish"
    DEEP-->>C: Starfish = Project Starfish<br/>(microservices migration, Q3)

    Note over C,HOT: Promote to Hot Cache
    C->>HOT: Add Starfish + DORA to CLAUDE.md<br/>(now resolves faster next time)
    C-->>U: Decoded request with full context
